-- Arizona Voter Law Requiring Citizenship Proof Invalidated by Appeals Court
-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 2010-10-26T17:26:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/arizona-voter-law-requiring-citizenship-proof-invalidated-by-appeals-court.html
An Arizona law requiring voters to
show proof of citizenship to register to vote is invalid, a
fedeal appeals court in San Francisco ruled today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
